6990	The following are the internal Lean helper declarations assembling the morphism
6991	module \cref{def:presheaf_internal_hom_value}, the slice internal hom
6992	\cref{def:presheaf_internal_hom}, its restriction maps
6993	\cref{lem:presheaf_internal_hom_restriction}, the presheaf dual
6994	\cref{def:presheaf_dual}, the evaluation morphism \cref{lem:internal_hom_eval}, the
6995	lax-monoidal restrict-scalars structure \cref{lem:restrictscalars_laxmonoidal}, the
6996	ring-iso base-change equivalence \cref{lem:restrictscalars_ringiso_tensorequiv} and
6997	the pushforward adjunction \cref{lem:presheaf_pushforward_adj_substrate}. Each is
6998	proved directly in Lean and carries the dependency edges of the construction.
